Gangsta Snowball
This is a game in the genre of top-down shooter

###### Install ######

1) GNU/Linux:
  OS ROSA - install package /Linux/gangsta.rpm

  Other OS:
  a) install the cocos2d engine (available in the repositories OS ROSA)
  http://python.cocos2d.org/download.html
  b) to install the library pyglet 1.2 (available in the repositories of all popular distributions)
  https://bitbucket.org/pyglet/pyglet/wiki/Home
  b) double clicking the left mouse button to start the file gangsta.py or,
  by typing in the terminal: python gangsta.py

###### Control ######

The keys W,A,S,D - control protagonist
R key - reloads current level
Frequent keystroke E - clears the pass, where there is a slide of snow that allow then to go to the next level.
!!!For the keypad you have to switch to English layout!!!

The mouse - sight
Left mouse button - shoot

